Mr. Roberto  TunioliDatalogic SpABologna, Italy, ItalyJoined Datalogic in 1988 as its financial director, becoming general manager in 1993 and CEO in 1995. Formerly worked in the financial services industry. An established and highly respected business leader in Italy and throughout Europe, in 2006 he received the 10th Italian edition of the Ernst & Young Entrepreneur of the Year award.2008 Third QuarterAdded to: Monster Worldwide Inc. - Weston, MAMonster provides online recruitment services. Revenues are $905 million.















 















 
















